### 租户管理 API 测试
### 使用 VS Code REST Client 插件运行

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### ==================== 创建租户 ====================

### 创建租户 - 企业
# @name create-tenant-enterprise
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "certificate_no": "91110000123456789X",
  "name": "测试公司",
  "type": 1,
  "contact_name": "张三",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "status": 1
}

### 创建租户 - 个人
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tenants HTTP/1.1  
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "certificate_no": "110101199001011234",
  "name": "李四",
  "type": 2,
  "contact_name": "李四",
  "email": "lisi@example.com",
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "status": 1
}

### ==================== 查询租户 ====================

### 分页查询租户列表
# @name list-tenants
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?page=1&page_size=10

### 分页查询 - 带关键字搜索
# @name search-by-keyword
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?keyword=测试&page=1&page_size=10

### 分页查询 - 按状态筛选
# @name filter-by-status
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?status=1&page=1&page_size=10

### 分页查询 - 按邮箱筛选
# @name filter-by-email
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?email=test@example.com&page=1&page_size=10

### 分页查询 - 按电话筛选
# @name filter-by-phone
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants?phone=13800138001&page=1&page_size=10

### 根据ID查询租户（替换为实际ID）
# @name get-tenant-by-id
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenants/your-tenant-id-here

### ==================== 更新租户 ====================

### 更新租户（部分更新，替换为实际ID）
# @name update-tenant
PUT {{baseUrl}}/tenants/your-tenant-id-here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的公司名",
  "contact_name": "王五",
  "status": 2
}

### ==================== 删除租户 ====================

### 删除租户（替换为实际ID）
# @name delete-tenant
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/tenants/your-tenant-id-here
